{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Visit_from_Drocal_Arconen",
  "title": "A Visit from Drocal Arconen",
  "summary": "Imperial Ambassador Morganna Tazecks, freshly recovered from being shot while addressing a crowd on KOS, briefs her nervous aide Bourne about an upcoming informal meeting with the Trandoshan ambassador Sscalyx before retreating to the embassy conference chamber to do paperwork. There she is surprised to find Minister of Imperial Commerce Drocal Arconen waiting, and their exchange turns into a chilly contest of wills: when Morganna's blunt, unprofessional candor irritates the Minister, he coldly reminds her of her place and she grudgingly submits to formality. Drocal explains he has come to Caspar to expand Imperial commercial ventures and demands her assistance, steering her toward the Caspian advisor Venus Darkstar -- once the Pretender's wife -- which prompts a furious outburst as he recounts how the Pretender mocked the true Emperor Palpatine before Drocal saw to his destruction. Recognizing a kindred capacity for violence and hatred in Morganna, Drocal softens enough to demand she share the story of her own brutal past before he departs, leaving her to her paperwork with an order to make time to recount her history.",
